The image depicts a large, rectangular signboard with a black background and gold-colored text. The signboard is mounted on a stone base, which appears to be made of a light-colored granite or marble. The text on the signboard is written in Chinese characters, and it reads as follows:

- The top line reads "谷大村" (Gǔ Dà Cūn), which translates to "Gu Da Village."
- The second line reads "原名：浴陵大愿" (Yuán Míng: Yù Líng Dà Yuàn), which translates to "Former Name: Yu Ling Da Yuan."
